ion-api-incubator/2.15.0-alpha/execution-metrics.json` still records overall `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, `generated_loc: 0`, and unchanged start/end commit `5e7655dd85fbfce1374ff00cb9863254de0cd1a7`, and the preserved branch currently does not contain the generated `tests/src/.../2.15.0-alpha` test project anymore.\n\nNext steps:\n1. Restore the missing `tests/src/io.opentelemetry.instrumentation/opentelemetry-instrumentation-api-incubator/2.15.0-alpha/` test project on the preserved branch and reapply the small API rename/type-parameter patch from `pi-generation-2026-05-05T05-24-44-252430Z.log`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.opentelemetry.instrumentation:opentelemetry-instrumentation-api-incubator:2.15.0-alpha` to confirm the restored test matches the passing reruns.\n3. If that passes, investigate why the automation recorded `generated_loc: 0` and preserved only logs/metrics instead of the fixed sources."}}
